<body class="fod_site">
	<div class="local home_temp">
		<div class="title">
			<p>Font of Data</p>
		</div>
		<div class="greeting_container">
			<div class="greeting primary Neutral">
				<h1 style="text-align: center;">Welcome to Font of Data!</h1>
				<p>Thank you for joining us during our playtesting phase! Please bear in mind that this game is still
					very much in development, and as you play or look around the site you are sure to run into things
					which aren't implemented, aren't finished, or are just placeholders for something better down the
					line. If you do encounter any issues whose scope seems to extend beyond what's mentioned above, please
					feel free to let us know! We have bug report links and social media pages coming, but for now you can
					drop a message on slack to @mwooden or @palatorr explaining the issue you found and we'll look into it.
					We appreciate your patience as we build this game and site, and thank you again for participating in
					this important stage of development.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tips primary Neutral">
			<h1 style="text-align: center;">Getting Started:</h1>
			<p>• For this first playtest, the three factions are mechanically identical. The special abilities are coming in later builds.</p>
			<p>• Click the question mark in the top right to activate tutorial mode.</p>
			<p>• Spend your data on connections between the nodes to increase the speed they expand your territory.</p>
			<p>• Spend your keys to begin new clusters from any unclaimed node.</p>
			<p>• The developers will be walking around answering questions and taking feedback, so feel free to flag one of us down.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="alerts secondary Neutral">
			<h1 style="text-align: center">Alerts</h1>
			<p>The next patch is not currently scheduled. Patches and maintinence will be announced here a week
				in advance, barring an issue which requires an immediate fix.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
